:
"使用 Skill 模板创建站点，上传文件"
,
"en"
:
"Create a site using a Skill template, uploading a file"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x hub site create --skill <skillId> --title <title> --data <json> <file>"
,
"cn"
:
"创建站点并附带结构化数据"
,
"en"
:
"Create a site with structured data"
}
]
}
,
"ls|list"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"列出当前用户的所有站点，返回站点 ID、标题、Skill、分享链接、版本数和最后更新时间"
,
"en"
:
"List all sites of the current user, returning ID, title, Skill, share URL, version count, and last updated time"
}
,
"--json|-j"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"以 JSON 格式输出"
,
