,
{
"cmd"
:
"x hub site ls --json"
,
"cn"
:
"以 JSON 格式列出所有站点"
,
"en"
:
"List all sites in JSON format"
}
]
}
,
"info"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"查看站点详情，返回：\n- 基本信息（ID、标题、Skill、分享链接）\n- currentData：当前版本的结构化数据\n- versions：版本列表（最新在前），包含版本 ID 和创建时间\n可通过版本列表获取 versionId，用于 rollback 回滚操作。\n"
,
"en"
:
"View site details, returning:\n- Basic info (ID, title, Skill, share URL)\n- currentData: structured data of the current version\n- versions: version list (newest first) with version ID and creation time\nUse version IDs from the list for rollback operations.\n"
}
,
"--json|-j"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"以 JSON 格式输出"
,
"en"
:
"Output in JSON format"
}
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"站点 ID（从 `x hub site ls` 获取）"
,
"en"
:
"Site ID (from `x hub site ls`)"
}
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x hub site info <siteId>"
,
"cn"
:
"查看站点详情和版本历史"
,
"en"
:
"View site details and version history"
}
]
}
,
"update"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"为站点上传新版本。新版本创建后自动成为当前展示版本，分享链接不变。\n相当于对站点内容进行更新，用户访问分享链接时会看到最新版本。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Upload a new version for the site. The new version automatically becomes the current displayed version, share URL remains unchanged.\nThis effectively updates the site content — visitors see the latest version via the share link.\n"
}
,
"--data|-d"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"该版本的结构化数据（JSON 字符串）。会覆盖之前的 data，用于记录本次更新的用户数据。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Structured data for this version (JSON string). Overwrites previous data, used to record user data for this update.\n"
}
,
"#1"
:
null
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"站点 ID"
,
"en"
:
"Site ID"
}
}
,
"#2"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"新版本的 HTML/ZIP 文件路径。最大 5MB。"
,
"en"
:
"HTML/ZIP file path for the new version. Max 5MB."
}
,
"#exec"
:
"___x_cmd_advise__file"
}
,
