:
"删除站点。软删除，分享链接将立即失效。此操作不可恢复。"
,
"en"
:
"Delete a site. Soft delete, the share link will be invalidated immediately. This action cannot be undone."
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"站点 ID"
,
"en"
:
"Site ID"
}
}
